title: Jim Mora might be helping Josh Rosen, Giants draft bluff on Barkley (Football 04/03)
description:
Jason La Canfora joins Will Brinson to talk about why the Giants might be bluffing with their interest in Saquon Barkley, why Jim Mora is actually helping Josh Rosen with his comments on his old quarterback, what the Browns and John Dorsey are thinking at the top of the draft, who the 2018 NFL Cinderella will be, whether the Gronk rumors are legitimate and what's going on with the Panthers sale. Bonus: The Orioles fantasy baseball advice you desperately crave.
